OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fcloudy with rain at times across the
OL,7,Fwest, heavy at times. Drier across the
OL,8,Feast with a few clear periods in the
OL,9,Fnortheast. Mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FLittle change, further rain
OL,12,Fat times in the west and north,
OL,13,Fbecoming more widespread and heavy in
OL,14,Fthe afternoon. Drier in the east with
OL,15,Fa little brightness at times. Mild.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FShowers or longer spells of rain on
OL,19,FThursday. Colder on Friday with
OL,20,Fshowers, these mainly in the west.
OL,21,FFurther rain expected on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
